        {
            "title": "英國改革黨領袖否認擬與保守黨結盟 誓言要令其喪失全國性政黨地位",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Nigel Farage\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FhHfj6V4I_JZWRaHEN_xjA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/996b261a65ead72317229f23229b6a22\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Nigel Farage</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 英國改革黨領袖奈傑爾·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:法拉奇;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/法拉奇\">法拉奇</a>駁斥了關於他正與<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:保守黨;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/保守黨\">保守黨</a>籌劃選舉聯盟的報導，相反誓言要徹底瓦解英國這一主要反對黨作為選舉力量的存在。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國《金融時報》周二晚間報導稱，法拉奇曾向捐助者表示，他預計在2029年中的下次大選前，將與Kemi Badenoch領導的保守黨達成一項協議或合併。但這位民粹主義領袖在X平台發文反駁，稱報導「有誤」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"奈傑爾·法拉奇攝影：Jason Alden/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/R1qU0dCZHr8iqRxqHyu7.w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b1ac60da0cd1c4d54a1805f3b65463b6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">奈傑爾·法拉奇攝影：Jason Alden/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「經歷了14年的欺騙與謊言後，他們永遠不配被原諒，」法拉奇如此評價2010-2024年間執政的保守黨。「說我會與他們合作的想法簡直荒謬。」 他補充稱，改革黨將在明年5月地方選舉中「確保保守黨喪失全國性政黨地位」。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cda98873-226d-3324-9c3f-74ff4ef6f759-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然僅有五名國會議員，但改革黨自4月起便穩居民調榜首。然而，鑒於民調顯示五大全國性政黨的支持率均為兩位數，下屆大選的勝者很可能需要結盟才能執政。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Farage Denies Tory Pact Reports Amid Fears He Can’t Win Majority</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Lucy White、Harry Wilson、James Woolcock.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%93%AC%E8%88%87%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E9%BB%A8%E7%B5%90%E7%9B%9F-%E8%AA%93%E8%A8%80%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%E5%85%B6%E5%96%AA%E5%A4%B1%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%80%A7%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D-114940221.html",
