        {
            "title": "比利時拒絕歐盟動用俄羅斯資產援助烏克蘭的計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 比利時否決了歐盟動用被凍結俄羅斯資產為烏克蘭貸款提供支持的新法律提案。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟委員會預計將在數小時後發布一項立法提案，授權歐盟動用高達2100億歐元（2440億美元）的俄羅斯央行凍結資產，為烏克蘭貸款提供支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「歐盟委員會今日將提交的文本未能令人滿意地解決我們的關切，」比利時外交大臣Maxime Prevot周三上午在北約會議前表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一意外否決為歐盟為烏克蘭尋找新融資方案的努力再添變數。而隨著基輔未來數月面臨現金短缺危機，官員們正面臨時間緊迫的困境。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8638e5ea-cde8-3663-b6a2-df65f5565724-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟多數領導人長期以來一直認為，動用俄羅斯資產是為烏克蘭籌集所需資金最可行的途徑。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但比利時數周來一直持反對態度，因大部分資金存放在布魯塞爾的歐洲清算銀行，該國擔憂可能面臨的法律後果。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府擔心若俄羅斯採取法律行動，比利時可能被迫承擔償還貸款的責任。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Prevot表示，「動用這筆資金卻讓我們獨自承擔風險的做法不可接受。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Belgium Rejects EU Plan to Tap Russian Assets for Ukraine (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Aaron Eglitis.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%94%E5%88%A9%E6%99%82%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E5%8B%95%E7%94%A8%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E6%8F%B4%E5%8A%A9%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-114455414.html",
