        {
            "title": "上海加強網上房地產信息監管 對社交媒體唱衰樓市等信息加大治理",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"上海加強網上房地產信息監管 對社交媒體唱衰樓市等信息加大治理\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5CX3HVMo3J5UcbMsco6emA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/30034160-c66d-11f0-bbff-e4d637aa1626\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">上海加強網上房地產信息監管 對社交媒體唱衰樓市等信息加大治理</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
